WEBVTT

00:00:00.440 --> 00:00:03.110
Good morning, family, and welcome to my

00:00:03.120 --> 00:00:06.269
channel where Jesus is King. I want you

00:00:06.279 --> 00:00:08.750
all to say this with me: 'For the Lord is

00:00:08.760 --> 00:00:12.990
good and His mercy endures

00:00:12.990 --> 00:00:13.000
forever.'For

00:00:13.000 --> 00:00:17.070
the Lord is good and His mercy endures

00:00:17.080 --> 00:00:20.590
forever.

00:00:24.320 --> 00:00:27.029
I have a word for you

00:00:27.029 --> 00:00:27.039
all;

00:00:27.039 --> 00:00:29.470
this is part two of what the Lord showed

00:00:29.480 --> 00:00:33.510
me in the one-hour vision that He

00:00:33.520 --> 00:00:37.630
gave me. So, I'm going to tell you all:

00:00:37.640 --> 00:00:39.590
you have the Holy Spirit living on the

00:00:39.600 --> 00:00:41.990
inside of you and He will show you

00:00:42.000 --> 00:00:44.510
things to come, too. I'm a Watchman and

00:00:44.520 --> 00:00:46.790
I'm telling you what I feel the Holy

00:00:46.800 --> 00:00:49.110
Spirit has told me.

00:00:49.120 --> 00:00:52.310
We are imperfect vessels that

00:00:52.320 --> 00:00:54.029
are getting a message from a

00:00:54.039 --> 00:00:56.430
perfect God. Whenever we're getting

00:00:56.440 --> 00:01:00.470
the download, the water is pure, but because it

00:01:00.470 --> 00:01:00.480
is going

00:01:00.480 --> 00:01:03.950
into an

00:01:03.950 --> 00:01:03.960
imperfect vessel,

00:01:03.960 --> 00:01:08.070
the pipe may be flawed.

00:01:08.080 --> 00:01:10.630
Because of that, it makes the

00:01:10.640 --> 00:01:13.870
water seem flawed

00:01:13.870 --> 00:01:13.880
as

00:01:13.880 --> 00:01:15.590
it

00:01:15.590 --> 00:01:15.600
goes

00:01:15.600 --> 00:01:18.190
through a pipe that's messed up.

00:01:18.190 --> 00:01:18.200
When

00:01:18.200 --> 00:01:20.149
God is downloading something

00:01:20.159 --> 00:01:22.870
into an imperfect vessel and we're

00:01:22.880 --> 00:01:24.749
relaying His

00:01:24.759 --> 00:01:28.630
message, the water's pure, but because the

00:01:28.640 --> 00:01:30.749
water's going through a pipe that

00:01:30.759 --> 00:01:33.310
could have some issues, it makes the

00:01:33.320 --> 00:01:36.069
water sometimes seem messed up—not that

00:01:36.069 --> 00:01:36.079
the water is

00:01:36.079 --> 00:01:37.710
messed up, but because the

00:01:37.720 --> 00:01:41.350
pipe is. I do

00:01:41.360 --> 00:01:43.709
the best I can; I'm a work in

00:01:43.719 --> 00:01:46.350
progress. We know that God is

00:01:46.360 --> 00:01:48.749
merciful, and I'm going to do the best I

00:01:48.759 --> 00:01:51.830
can to tell you what I saw in the spirit without

00:01:51.830 --> 00:01:51.840
adding

00:01:51.840 --> 00:01:53.590
to or taking away

00:01:53.600 --> 00:01:57.630
from anything. This is again

00:01:57.640 --> 00:02:00.109
just me

00:02:00.109 --> 00:02:00.119
being

00:02:00.119 --> 00:02:02.550
transparent to you all about exactly what I'm

00:02:02.560 --> 00:02:05.510
doing for my family and what I believe

00:02:05.520 --> 00:02:09.109
that we should do. I believe,

00:02:09.119 --> 00:02:11.790
with what He has shown me regarding the coming

00:02:11.800 --> 00:02:14.830
food supply, that you

00:02:14.840 --> 00:02:17.430
need to have a storehouse. The Lord

00:02:17.440 --> 00:02:18.990
said

00:02:19.000 --> 00:02:22.309
to me, 'Brandon, you need to get your

00:02:22.319 --> 00:02:24.670
boat ready; you need to get your

00:02:24.680 --> 00:02:27.229
storehouse ready. You need to have this

00:02:27.239 --> 00:02:29.990
stuff set aside and prepared for your

00:02:29.990 --> 00:02:30.000
family.'That's

00:02:30.000 --> 00:02:33.350
what He said

00:02:33.360 --> 00:02:35.589
to me. Now, for you, I don't

00:02:35.589 --> 00:02:35.599
know—everybody's

00:02:35.599 --> 00:02:38.470
situation is

00:02:38.470 --> 00:02:38.480
different—but

00:02:38.480 --> 00:02:40.270
He said to me, 'I want you to

00:02:40.280 --> 00:02:41.990
get your stuff ready for your

00:02:41.990 --> 00:02:42.000
family.'What

00:02:42.000 --> 00:02:44.670
I heard Him say is

00:02:44.670 --> 00:02:44.680
to

00:02:44.680 --> 00:02:48.229
have some cash on hand, have some food

00:02:48.239 --> 00:02:51.830
on hand,

00:02:51.830 --> 00:02:51.840
and

00:02:51.840 --> 00:02:54.309
have several weeks of

00:02:54.309 --> 00:02:54.319
bottled

00:02:54.319 --> 00:02:56.830
water stored up for your family.

00:02:56.840 --> 00:02:59.149
That's what He said to me. So I went

00:02:59.159 --> 00:03:01.229
and I'm trying to get all this stuff;

00:03:01.239 --> 00:03:02.910
it's going to take time.

00:03:02.920 --> 00:03:05.630
He said, 'Brandon, I will take care of

00:03:08.239 --> 00:03:11.270
My kids, but what you can

00:03:11.280 --> 00:03:15.390
do is prepare for what you

00:03:15.390 --> 00:03:15.400
need.'If

00:03:15.400 --> 00:03:17.030
you don't

00:03:17.040 --> 00:03:18.670
have anything and you don't have any

00:03:18.680 --> 00:03:20.869
money, that's fine;

00:03:20.879 --> 00:03:22.470
God's going to take care of you. But in

00:03:22.480 --> 00:03:25.309
my situation, I had some extra, and I want

00:03:25.319 --> 00:03:26.869
to say, 'Hey, listen, I'm going to get some

00:03:26.879 --> 00:03:29.110
food for the five of

00:03:29.110 --> 00:03:29.120
us.'I

00:03:29.120 --> 00:03:30.990
have three

00:03:31.000 --> 00:03:32.830
kids and two adults in this house, and I

00:03:32.840 --> 00:03:34.350
believe if you can have a

00:03:34.360 --> 00:03:37.350
week or two weeks'worth of food, it's smart.

00:03:37.360 --> 00:03:38.990
It's not something

00:03:39.000 --> 00:03:41.229
I'm going to hoard;

00:03:42.799 --> 00:03:45.309
you can

00:03:45.309 --> 00:03:45.319
rotate

00:03:45.319 --> 00:03:47.990
it out as you go and

00:03:48.000 --> 00:03:49.630
then replenish it.

00:03:49.630 --> 00:03:49.640
Canned

00:03:49.640 --> 00:03:52.630
tuna or whatever

00:03:52.640 --> 00:03:54.670
lasts for a while, but whenever it

00:03:54.680 --> 00:03:56.750
gets ready to expire, eat it.

00:03:58.799 --> 00:04:00.390
Then the other thing was

00:04:00.400 --> 00:04:04.390
He spoke to me about

00:04:04.400 --> 00:04:08.190
tradable things, like if your

00:04:08.200 --> 00:04:12.589
neighbor had a chicken and you had

00:04:12.589 --> 00:04:12.599
an

00:04:12.599 --> 00:04:14.509
ounce of silver and you offered

00:04:14.509 --> 00:04:14.519
that

00:04:14.519 --> 00:04:15.750
ounce

00:04:15.760 --> 00:04:18.390
of silver for the chicken or some

00:04:18.400 --> 00:04:20.749
vegetables. That's what He

00:04:20.759 --> 00:04:22.469
was showing me in the spirit

00:04:22.479 --> 00:04:25.110
for my family. He talked to me about

00:04:25.120 --> 00:04:28.469
gas mileage and having a car that

00:04:28.479 --> 00:04:31.830
gets 30 or 40 miles to a gallon.

00:04:31.840 --> 00:04:34.230
Right now, I have an SUV and it drinks

00:04:34.240 --> 00:04:37.110
a lot of gas. So if you have the means to

00:04:37.120 --> 00:04:39.430
get a Honda or a Toyota,

00:04:39.440 --> 00:04:41.790
that would be a wise

00:04:41.800 --> 00:04:43.230
decision.

00:04:43.240 --> 00:04:44.990
I'm not

00:04:45.000 --> 00:04:47.710
big on electric cars. I had one for a

00:04:47.720 --> 00:04:49.870
while and I did not like it;

00:04:49.880 --> 00:04:52.350
it was awful to try to charge,

00:04:52.360 --> 00:04:54.150
taking

00:04:54.160 --> 00:04:56.790
45 minutes for a full charge,

00:04:56.800 --> 00:04:59.230
and you

00:04:59.240 --> 00:05:01.550
couldn't go very far on

00:05:01.550 --> 00:05:01.560
it

00:05:01.560 --> 00:05:04.550
anyway. We got half of

00:05:04.560 --> 00:05:06.150
the

00:05:06.160 --> 00:05:08.590
recommended battery life,

00:05:08.600 --> 00:05:10.390
especially when it was hot

00:05:10.400 --> 00:05:12.710
or cold. If it was extremely

00:05:12.720 --> 00:05:14.749
cold,

00:05:14.759 --> 00:05:16.790
you could see the battery

00:05:16.800 --> 00:05:18.510
moving; it was

00:05:18.520 --> 00:05:19.990
freaking me out.

00:05:22.160 --> 00:05:24.150
In hot times, the

00:05:24.160 --> 00:05:25.830
air conditioner sucks the battery big

00:05:25.840 --> 00:05:29.189
time. So,

00:05:32.720 --> 00:05:36.590
having a car

00:05:36.600 --> 00:05:38.830
that gets good gas mileage is wise. If you can,

00:05:38.840 --> 00:05:41.950
ask your doctor

00:05:41.960 --> 00:05:44.909
about your medication

00:05:44.909 --> 00:05:44.919
and

00:05:44.919 --> 00:05:47.870
have

00:05:47.880 --> 00:05:51.350
enough to get

00:05:51.360 --> 00:05:53.790
you through a week or two extra just in

00:05:53.800 --> 00:05:56.590
case there's a shortage. I saw

00:05:56.600 --> 00:06:00.590
shortages of certain medications coming

00:06:00.600 --> 00:06:04.790
because of trade wars with China.

00:06:04.800 --> 00:06:07.430
When they go against

00:06:07.440 --> 00:06:09.870
Taiwan and the United States is upset,

00:06:09.880 --> 00:06:11.950
I

00:06:11.960 --> 00:06:16.550
saw prescription

00:06:16.550 --> 00:06:16.560
medications—some

00:06:16.560 --> 00:06:20.350
kinds, not all—becoming very

00:06:20.360 --> 00:06:24.469
hard to get. If you have to have

00:06:24.479 --> 00:06:26.029
blood pressure medicine,

00:06:26.039 --> 00:06:28.189
diabetic medicine, or

00:06:28.199 --> 00:06:30.230
heart medicine, maybe you

00:06:30.240 --> 00:06:32.830
can talk to your doctor and say, 'Listen,

00:06:32.840 --> 00:06:36.070
Doc, I need an extra one to two weeks

00:06:36.080 --> 00:06:39.870
ahead of

00:06:39.870 --> 00:06:39.880
time.'If

00:06:39.880 --> 00:06:41.469
you have out-of-pocket money,

00:06:41.479 --> 00:06:43.469
just buy it.

00:06:43.479 --> 00:06:45.070
I'm not a doctor;

00:06:45.080 --> 00:06:46.790
I'm just trying to put some

00:06:46.800 --> 00:06:48.550
ideas out there for those

00:06:48.550 --> 00:06:48.560
who

00:06:48.560 --> 00:06:50.270
really

00:06:50.280 --> 00:06:51.790
desperately need it.

00:06:53.240 --> 00:06:55.430
I believe Jesus is a

00:06:55.440 --> 00:06:57.469
healer and that God is going to

00:06:57.479 --> 00:06:58.950
take care of you anyway,

00:07:04.160 --> 00:07:06.189
but I'm just

00:07:06.199 --> 00:07:08.990
saying some people's faith is not there.

00:07:09.000 --> 00:07:11.430
Some

00:07:11.440 --> 00:07:13.869
people do not know how to believe God

00:07:13.879 --> 00:07:16.909
for two pennies, let alone to stay

00:07:16.919 --> 00:07:18.350
alive, because they've not

00:07:18.360 --> 00:07:21.510
grown their faith. It's not

00:07:21.520 --> 00:07:23.550
condemnation; there is no

00:07:23.560 --> 00:07:25.510
condemnation for those who are in Christ

00:07:25.520 --> 00:07:27.790
Jesus. I'm not here trying to scare

00:07:27.800 --> 00:07:30.150
you; I'm trying to prepare you.

00:07:32.199 --> 00:07:34.390
We are in the end times and labor

00:07:34.400 --> 00:07:36.990
pains are coming even greater in the

00:07:37.000 --> 00:07:39.990
days ahead. It

00:07:39.990 --> 00:07:40.000
is

00:07:40.000 --> 00:07:43.469
something to

00:07:43.469 --> 00:07:43.479
take

00:07:43.479 --> 00:07:45.670
precaution about.

00:07:45.680 --> 00:07:48.390
I told you about having big screws

00:07:48.400 --> 00:07:49.950
in your doors;

00:07:49.960 --> 00:07:52.469
I'm just trying to slow the

00:07:52.479 --> 00:07:55.790
bad guys down. I saw people looting

00:07:55.800 --> 00:07:58.990
houses and robbing homes in major

00:07:59.000 --> 00:08:00.029
cities

00:08:00.039 --> 00:08:03.869
when the economy crashes and things go

00:08:03.879 --> 00:08:07.909
to pot. I saw people

00:08:10.510 --> 00:08:10.520
rioting

00:08:12.080 --> 00:08:13.909
because Social Security was

00:08:13.919 --> 00:08:16.270
cut off for a while, along with government

00:08:16.280 --> 00:08:18.189
funding and food stamps. It

00:08:18.199 --> 00:08:21.710
was bad. People were

00:08:21.710 --> 00:08:21.720
rioting,

00:08:21.720 --> 00:08:23.110
and like I said, during the

00:08:23.110 --> 00:08:23.120
COVID

00:08:23.120 --> 00:08:25.189
when all those people were

00:08:25.199 --> 00:08:28.149
acting crazy for toilet paper, just think

00:08:28.159 --> 00:08:30.790
about the grocery store shelves. I

00:08:30.800 --> 00:08:33.389
told everybody that there was no food on

00:08:33.399 --> 00:08:35.829
the shelves—there were cobwebs—and it

00:08:35.839 --> 00:08:37.670
happened that fast. They had to

00:08:37.680 --> 00:08:39.870
combine what was in one store

00:08:39.880 --> 00:08:41.509
to another store

00:08:41.509 --> 00:08:41.519
at

00:08:41.519 --> 00:08:43.389
a central location with armed

00:08:43.399 --> 00:08:45.829
guards so you couldn't

00:08:45.839 --> 00:08:47.750
rob the grocery store.

00:08:50.080 --> 00:08:52.550
People need to

00:08:52.560 --> 00:08:54.230
understand that when you can't feed your

00:08:54.240 --> 00:08:58.430
family, people act stupid.

00:08:58.440 --> 00:09:00.710
I

00:09:00.720 --> 00:09:02.310
believe in the Second Amendment

00:09:02.320 --> 00:09:04.069
personally. You say, 'Would you shoot

00:09:04.079 --> 00:09:05.670
somebody for food?'If you're

00:09:05.680 --> 00:09:06.910
going to come into my house and try to

00:09:06.920 --> 00:09:08.630
hurt me, yes, I'm going to have to

00:09:08.640 --> 00:09:10.630
defend my family. But if you're

00:09:10.640 --> 00:09:13.110
asking for a cup of rice, I'll do what I

00:09:13.120 --> 00:09:15.430
can. My family comes first.

00:09:15.440 --> 00:09:17.949
If

00:09:17.959 --> 00:09:19.670
you haven't taken the means to provide

00:09:19.680 --> 00:09:21.310
for yourself, why are you going to try to

00:09:21.320 --> 00:09:23.190
take from me? It's like the old hen that

00:09:23.200 --> 00:09:24.949
got all the grain and worked

00:09:24.959 --> 00:09:26.790
hard, and then everybody came and tried

00:09:37.200 --> 00:09:39.069
to eat her

00:09:39.079 --> 00:09:40.550
bread. She did all the hard work and set it aside for her chicks, but then the dog and everyone else in the story tried to eat her bread and she said, 'No, this

00:09:40.560 --> 00:09:42.470
is for me,'because they didn't put in the

00:09:42.480 --> 00:09:44.550
work.

00:09:49.839 --> 00:09:53.670
It's not always our job to

00:09:53.680 --> 00:09:55.269
feed everybody; you've got to make sure your family

00:09:55.269 --> 00:09:55.279
is

00:09:55.279 --> 00:09:57.350
taken care of, too.

00:10:01.320 --> 00:10:03.710
I'm going to go

00:10:03.720 --> 00:10:05.829
back to the vision where the Lord

00:10:05.839 --> 00:10:07.590
spoke to me and showed me this

00:10:07.600 --> 00:10:09.470
open-eyed.

00:10:09.480 --> 00:10:10.870
He said, 'Brandon, this is

00:10:10.880 --> 00:10:13.030
going to last and be a lot harder than

00:10:13.040 --> 00:10:15.630
what people realize. They are not taking

00:10:15.640 --> 00:10:18.150
it seriously.'He said it

00:10:18.150 --> 00:10:18.160
would

00:10:18.160 --> 00:10:20.069
be an extended time

00:10:20.069 --> 00:10:20.079
and

00:10:20.079 --> 00:10:22.269
that

00:10:22.269 --> 00:10:22.279
it

00:10:22.279 --> 00:10:25.630
will not be prayed away. He

00:10:25.640 --> 00:10:28.069
said there's a shaking to

00:10:28.079 --> 00:10:30.069
awaken

00:10:30.079 --> 00:10:33.430
coming. In this humbling,

00:10:33.430 --> 00:10:33.440
it

00:10:33.440 --> 00:10:36.269
will bring a great revival. People

00:10:36.279 --> 00:10:38.870
are asking for revival but

00:10:38.870 --> 00:10:38.880
they

00:10:38.880 --> 00:10:40.949
are

00:10:40.959 --> 00:10:42.430
stiff-necked,

00:10:42.440 --> 00:10:44.310
arrogant, and pompous. There is a

00:10:44.320 --> 00:10:46.550
remnant of people that God is wanting to

00:10:46.560 --> 00:10:49.030
call; this is

00:10:49.040 --> 00:10:51.790
the last call.

00:10:53.720 --> 00:10:56.870
Are you one that's going to

00:10:56.880 --> 00:11:00.230
run to the Father? Out of mercy,

00:11:00.240 --> 00:11:04.230
I'm telling you, we will not be a

00:11:04.240 --> 00:11:07.670
goat nation. He said the prayers of our

00:11:07.680 --> 00:11:10.790
founding fathers still go before Him and

00:11:10.800 --> 00:11:14.590
what is coming is not

00:11:14.590 --> 00:11:14.600
His

00:11:14.600 --> 00:11:18.069
judgment, but a shaking

00:11:18.069 --> 00:11:18.079
to

00:11:18.079 --> 00:11:21.269
wake

00:11:21.279 --> 00:11:25.389
up the people, for they are asleep.

00:11:30.920 --> 00:11:33.949
I saw no

00:11:33.959 --> 00:11:35.710
denominational

00:11:35.710 --> 00:11:35.720
barriers—Baptist,

00:11:35.720 --> 00:11:40.310
Methodist, Catholic,

00:11:40.310 --> 00:11:40.320
Episcopalian—everybody

00:11:40.320 --> 00:11:43.829
came

00:11:43.839 --> 00:11:47.509
together as one,

00:11:47.519 --> 00:11:51.030
similar to how everybody came

00:11:51.040 --> 00:11:53.990
together in World War II

00:11:53.990 --> 00:11:54.000
when

00:11:54.000 --> 00:11:55.829
women worked in the factories

00:11:55.839 --> 00:11:58.790
just to keep everything afloat. Everybody pitched

00:11:58.790 --> 00:11:58.800
in

00:11:58.800 --> 00:12:02.870
as an American

00:12:02.880 --> 00:12:05.230
to keep our country going.

00:12:07.079 --> 00:12:10.389
That's the way

00:12:10.399 --> 00:12:13.310
I saw the body of Christ

00:12:13.320 --> 00:12:17.590
coming together as one, no

00:12:17.600 --> 00:12:21.829
longer

00:12:21.839 --> 00:12:24.350
about

00:12:24.350 --> 00:12:24.360
charismatics

00:12:24.360 --> 00:12:26.389
or

00:12:26.399 --> 00:12:27.990
seeker-friendlies,

00:12:27.990 --> 00:12:28.000
but

00:12:28.000 --> 00:12:29.710
the

00:12:29.720 --> 00:12:32.069
body of Christ because people were

00:12:32.079 --> 00:12:34.710
desperate.

00:12:34.720 --> 00:12:36.629
It was beautiful because

00:12:36.639 --> 00:12:37.509
we

00:12:37.519 --> 00:12:40.629
operated in love. Walking

00:12:40.629 --> 00:12:40.639
in

00:12:40.639 --> 00:12:43.230
love

00:12:43.230 --> 00:12:43.240
is

00:12:43.240 --> 00:12:45.189
going to bring forth the glory. If

